  "text": "As indicated above, one wants to assign representations of the the vertex algebra V to the marked points of Σ. Representations M of the vertex algebra V must in particular be representations of the Lie-algebra U ′ (V ) generated from the coefficients A n , see [CITATION_1] Section 5] for more details.",
